ated just minutes from orlando’s famous theme parks including walt disney world sea world and universal orlando despite being so close to some of the world’s most popular attractions the area maintains a small town charming atmosphere centered around the lake butler chain windermere offers aquatic recreation at every turn residents enjoy bass fishing water skiing wakeboarding and boating against a backdrop of elegant estates that are home to famous sports personalities and recording artists learn more winter garden ranked as one of the fastest growing suburbs by forbescom winter garden florida offers something for everyone residents fondly consider the city a “modernday mayberry usa” due to humble citrus town roots but the area is becoming a major destination thanks to the countless local attractions just twenty minutes west of orlando winter garden boasts a top regional farmer’s market winter garden village at fowlers grove openair shopping center with more than ninety stores and a training facility for the orlando solar bears hockey team learn more clermont windermere winter garden beazer communities in none selected price  high to low price  low to high sq ft  high to low sq ft  low to high harvest landing single family homes from  sq ft    beds    baths    community details driving directions quick movein homes available windermere isle  estate series single family homes from  sq ft    beds    baths    community details driving directions quick movein homes available windermere isle  manor series single family homes from  sq ft    beds    baths    community details driving directions windermere trails single family homes from  sq ft    beds    baths    community details driving directions quick movein homes available orchard hills single family homes from  sq ft    beds    baths    community details driving directions quick movein homes available summerlake single family single family homes from  sq ft    beds    baths    community details driving directions qui