titure merger consolidation or asset sale  updating contact information and optout choices we give customers control over their personal information we provide you with access to your personal information in various ways including statements and community mailings and want you to make sure that the personal information we have about you is accurate and current beazer homes enables users of its website to update contact information and to opt out of the collection of personally identifiable information or particular communications or services you may do so by going to this optout link or by contacting us at  or homeinfobeazercom due to production mailing and system timelines it may take some time to process your request in addition we may still use your information to communicate with you for other purposes such as for customer service  questions or comments if you have any questions or comments about this policy please contact us at  or homeinfobeazercom  miscellaneous terms and conditions  this policy is subject to a part of and incorporated into the beazer homes terms and conditions changes and updates to this policy  please revisit this page periodically to stay aware of any changes to this policy which may be revised periodically at our sole discretion if we modify this policy we will make it available through the website and indicate the date of the latest revision in the event that the modifications materially alter your rights or obligations hereunder we will make reasonable efforts to notify you of the change for example we may send a message to your email address if we have one on file or generate a popup or similar notification when you signin to the website for the first time after such material changes are made our amended policy will automatically take effect  days after it is made available through the website except that i we generally only use your personally identifiable information in the manner described in the policy in effect when we received th