y ventura county sacramento county kern county yuba county and las vegas among others the companys east segment includes indiana marylanddelaware tennessee and virginia the markets under east segment include indianapolis baltimore howard anne arundel nashville loudoun county prince william county stafford county spotsylvania county and fredericksburg its southeast segment includes florida georgia north carolina and south carolina the markets under southeast segment include orlando atlanta charleston and myrtle beach » full overview of bzh company address beazer homes usa inc  abernathy rd ste atlanta   ga    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation brian beazer  allan merrill  robert salomon  kenneth khoury  peter orser  » more officers  directors beazer homes usa inc news briefbeazer homes reports qtrly total revenue of  million may   briefbeazer enters an agreement with mohawk to include all flooring categories apr   briefbeazer homes announces pricing of offering of  mln of senior unsecured notes mar   briefbeazer homes announces tender offer for pct senior notes mar   briefbeazer homes announces proposed offering of  mln of senior notes mar   » more bzh news related topics stocksstock screenerhomebuilding bzh stock price  beazer homes usa inc stock quote us nyse  marketwatch sections watchlist signup • login search bulletin via tweet president announces ban on transgender miltary service bulletin newhome sales tread water as supplystarved recovery lurches ahead in june bulletin us europe asia fx rates futures range d d m m m y y dow    sp     nasdaq    globaldow    gold    oil    sp  movers amd  ba  amp  t  akam  uhs  wynn  jnpr  latest newsall times eastern a breaking boeings record stock rally adds  points to dow a trump says administration to bar transgender individuals from serving in military a video replay would’ve cancelled out the ‘hand of god’ maradona says a updated what ever happened to inflation a updated dollar ticks up